@startuml
!define GCP #4285F4
!define APPENGINE #4285F4
!define BIGQUERY #4285F4
!define STORAGE #4285F4

actor Developer
participant "Local Environment" as Local
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "GCP App Engine" as AppEngine GCP
participant "GCP BigQuery" as BigQuery GCP
participant "GCP Cloud Storage" as Storage GCP

Developer -> Local : Clone repository
Developer -> Local : Install dependencies
Developer -> Local : Develop Dash app
Developer -> Local : Test locally
Developer -> Git : Push changes
Developer -> AppEngine : Deploy app (gcloud app deploy)
AppEngine -> AppEngine : Configure environment (app.yaml)
AppEngine -> BigQuery : Query data
AppEngine -> Storage : Fetch data
AppEngine -> AppEngine : Create visualizations
AppEngine -> AppEngine : Serve Dash app
@enduml